  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The main objective of this research is to demonstrate the possible use of erythroferrone
      (ERFE) as a potential marker of recombinant human erythropoietin (rHuEpo) use to be included
      in the Athlete Biological Passport (PBA) developed by the World Anti-Doping Agency (WADA).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
